body:
Atlas UI

Copy and paste the following query into the
Query Editor, and then click the Search
button in the Query Editor.

```json
[
  {
    $search: {
      autocomplete: {
        path: "title",
        query: "men with",
        tokenOrder: "sequential"
      }
    }
  }
]
```

MongoDB Shell

Each query includes a:

- [$limit](manual/reference/operator/aggregation/limit) stage to limit the output to 4 results.

- [$project](manual/reference/operator/aggregation/project) stage to exclude all fields except `title`.

```js
db.movies.aggregate([
  {
    $search: {
      "autocomplete": {
        "path": "title",
        "query": "men with",
        "tokenOrder": "sequential"
      }
    }
  },
  {
    $limit: 4
  },
  {
    $project: {
      "_id": 0,
      "title": 1
    }
  }
])

```

